---
layout: page
title: Blog
pagination:
    data: collections.posts
    size: 3
    alias: posts
    reverse: true
---
<h1>{{ title }}</h1>

<ul>
  {%- for post in posts | reverse -%}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}">"{{ post.title }}"</a> <i>(published {{ post.date }})</i></li>
      {% if post.data.teaser %}
        <p>{{ post.data.teaser }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </li>
  {%- endfor -%}
</ul>
---
<p>More posts can be found in <a href="{{ 'archive.html' | url }}">the archive</a>.</p>